3 Tex-Mex Flavor Bombs
Cashew Sour Cream 
2 tablespoons extra-virgin olive oil
2 cups (150g) thinly sliced cremini mushrooms
1 cup (90g) thinly sliced onion
1 cup (270g) thinly sliced red bell pepper
1/4 cup water
1 can black beans, drained and rinsed
1 or 2 ripe large avocados
6 medium soft tortillas
Chopped fresh cilantro
Sea salt
black pepper
Fresh lime juice
